<div class="container">
    
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to the @ViewData["Title"]</h1>
        <p>Your trusted partner in the Seattle real estate market.</p>
    </header>
    <main>
         <section>
            <p>Looking for your dream home or planning to sell your property in Seattle? 
                We are here to help. As the top real estate services in Seattle, WA,
                we offer unparalleled service for buyers, sellers, and renters. 
                Our dedicated team specializes in residential properties, providing expert 
                advice and personalized service to meet your unique needs. 
                With over 10 years of experience, 
                we make your real estate journey smooth and successful.
                Visit the Best Real Estate Services and contact us today for a free consultation 
                and experience the difference!                
            </p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <h2>Pay only for the best real estate services you need!</h2>
            <p class="offer">For <strong>$2,995*,</strong> get 1.5 hours of initial consultation, home listed in the NWMLS, sign, flyer box, key box, preliminary title, contract write up, and contract negotiation for a successful closing.</p>
            <p>You must also pay the buyer's agent commission & listing fee only applies to single-family homes priced $2M or less.</p>
            <p class="offer">If your home sells for <strong>$700,000,</strong>  you can save up to <strong>$18,000</strong> in commission.</p>
            <p class="offer">If your home sells for <strong>$1M,</strong>  you can save up to <strong>$27,000</strong> in commission.</p>
            
            <h2>Customer Information Form</h2>
            
            <form method="post">
                <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <label for="firstName">First Name:</label>
                            <input type="text" id="firstName" name="FirstName" class="input-control" required>
                        </div>                                    
                        <div class="col-md-4">                        
                            <label for="lastName">Last Name:</label>
                            <input type="text" id="lastName" name="LastName" class="input-control" required>
                        </div>
                </div>

                <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                            <label for="email">Email:</label>
                            <input type="email" id="email" name="Email" class="input-control" required>
                        </div>                                    
                        <div class="col-md-4">                        
                            <label for="phone">Phone Number:</label>
                            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="Phone" class="input-control" required>                    
                        </div>
                </div>
                                
                <label for="query">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="query" name="Query" class="input-control_textarea"></textarea>

                <div>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Submit</button>
                </div>
                
            </form>


