        <section>
            <h2>Buyers: Get REBATES on commission!</h2>
            <p class="offer">On a <strong>$700,000,</strong> home, you can get up to a <strong>$10,000</strong> rebate check in the mail after closing.</p>
            <p class="offer">On a <strong>$1M,</strong> home, you can get up to a <strong>$20,000</strong> rebate check in the mail after closing.</p>
